entries.title_d: Our spy didn't die in vain, he managed to transfer most of his important data to your ship before his unfortunate end. Bring it to one of our smugglers immediately.
entries.title: Dathomir system: Deliver the Vortex operatives data.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: The smuggler provided us with these coordinates. Try to avoid leading Imperial forces to this area if you can.
entries.quest_location_d: You will be doing a data run through extremely dangerous areas and we know that the Empire is looking for you so I hope you came prepared for a fight my friend.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Make sure that you have eliminated nearby Imperial threats before starting the docking sequence as both you and the smuggler will be very vulnerable while transferring the data.
entries.hello_d: Greetings, you got a package for me I'm told.
entries.found_loc_d: Lets make sure our operative didn't die in vain. Deliver the data he transferred to our smuggler at these coordinates.
entries.failed_destroyed: That poor smuggler just tried to help. Return to base immediately pilot, we need to talk.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Lets do this quickly, I don't like the look of all those laser burns on your ship.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Alright I got it and I'm out of here, be safe!
entries.attack_stopped: Tactical Computer: < No more fighter vessels within sensor range. >
entries.attack_notify: Tactical Computer: < Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed. >
entries.arrived_at_delivery: You are at the correct location pilot, the smuggler should be there any second.
